## Status Key

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| 🔴 Not started | Implementation not yet begun |
| 🟡 In progress | Partially implemented |
| 🟢 Complete | Implemented and tested against acceptance criterion |
| ⚫ Deferred | Moved to future scope |

